In the course search, the keyword search doesn't work unless you select something first. Specifically, you have to select the Training Type (e.g., Pilot, Management, Maintenance, or Technician), then select the Manufacturer (e.g., Cessna), and then select the Model — only then can you perform the search. However, it's not perfectly synced; sometimes it works, and sometimes it doesn't. So, at minimum, if you want to search by keyword, you need to select the category (Training Type), Manufacturer, and Model list first.
